Her eyes slowly opened, trying to adjust to the
dimness surrounding her.
The slender, white, overgrown squirrel clambered to
her feet, looking around.
'Where am I?' She wondered. 'And for that matter, WHO
am I?'
She went a few paces forward, feeling sick and dizzy.
"Somebody..help me.." She said feebly, stumbling along
the uneven ground.
